# MyMilesAI — Cloudflare Pages redirects
# Format: <source>  <destination>  <status>
# Takes effect after the Cloudflare Pages cutover.

# www → apex
https://www.mymilesai.com/*  https://mymilesai.com/:splat  301!

# Apple may also probe /apple-app-site-association at the root in addition
# to /.well-known/. Mirror so both paths resolve.
/apple-app-site-association  /.well-known/apple-app-site-association  200

